properties.Name: Task
properties.Description: A specific task or piece of work that is performed.

Columns.Name: TaskId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Task.

Columns.Name: TaskName
Columns.Description: The name of a Task.

Columns.Name: TaskDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskSpecificationStatement
Columns.Description:
Detailed statements of project deliverables that result from requirements definition and design. 

Specifications usually describe deliverables in terms of appearance, constraints and quality attributes. 

Specifications are the basis for acceptance criteria used in scope verification and quality control.

Columns.Name: SequenceNumber
Columns.Description: The sequence number of the Task.

Columns.Name: MilestoneIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the task is a milestone.

Columns.Name: CriticalPathTaskIndicator
Columns.Description: Tasks in a project network that have the longest duration. This represents the series of activities that determines the earliest completion of the project

Columns.Name: TaskNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the related Task.

Columns.Name: TaskPlannedStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The planned start timestamp of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskScheduledStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The scheduled start timestamp of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskActualStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual start date of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskPlannedCompletionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The planned completion timestamp of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskScheduledCompletionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The scheduled completion timestamp of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskActualCompletionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual finish date of the task.

Columns.Name: TaskEarliestStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The earliest task start timestamp.

Columns.Name: TaskLatestStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The latest task start timestamp.

Columns.Name: TaskEarliestCompletionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The earliest task completion timestamp.

Columns.Name: TaskLatestCompletionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The latest task completion timestamp.

Columns.Name: TaskFloatHours
Columns.Description: The amount of time available for a task to slip before it results in a delay of the project end date. It is the difference between the task's early and late start dates.

Columns.Name: PlannedBillableLaborUnits
Columns.Description: The planned total number of billable labor units anticipated to be associated with the task.

Columns.Name: ActualBillableLaborUnits
Columns.Description: The actual total number of billable labor units resulting from the task.

Columns.Name: PlannedBillableChargesAmount
Columns.Description: The planned total amount of billable charges anticipated to be associated with the task.

Columns.Name: ActualBillableChargesAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total amount of billable charges associated with the task.

Columns.Name: PlannedCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The planned internal costs associated with the task.

Columns.Name: ActualCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The actual internal costs associated with the task.

Columns.Name: TaskTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Task Type.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: ResponsibilityCenterId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Responsibility Center.

Columns.Name: TaskGlAccountNumber
Columns.Description: The GL Account Number assigned to a Task.

Properties.Description: A specific task or piece of work that is performed.
